NOTE: The reference model for aircondMulti is found in: ~/mpisppy/tests/examples/aircondMulti.py

This is a multi-product version of aircond. It is exercised via
mpisppy/generic_cylinders.py --module-name ../../mpisppy/tests/examples/aircondMulti
(see examples/run_all.py for the command line used in regression testing).

sample_tree_scen_creator is not yet implemented for aircondMulti, so
MMW / sequential-sampling confidence interval routines are not available
for this example.
